title: Games missing from match history
body: Hey I won with liss, lost with cait and just won with cho, but the games that I won aren't showing up in my match history. What's the deal?

replies.body: Looks like there may be some one-off issues on the backend with loading the game into match history, but it looks like the game did count and I'm seeing LP earned for that game.  Not sure to be honest if it'll make it into your match history later (usually would in this case though not guaranteed), but hopefully this helps clarify things a little bit.
I also had this issue with 2 games
the lissandra win is completely missing from my match history
